title: I deleted an old work app on Pixel 3 linked to my gmail. Now I can't use Google Maps or go to url-s?
content: I've turned on and off phone. When I try to go to a website, pixel says "No app found to open URL".  When I try to use Maps its says I'm offline even if I have full reception bars.
category: Connectivity, Network, Bluetooth, Google Pixel 3 XL
